text:
Thanks Marissa for setting up the bike challenge thing!! 

Every ride counts, even the ones outside of commuting. <https://www.lovetoride.net/oregon> 

FYI, you do not need to pay for signing up. Supporting the cause is good but simply writing $0 in the donation field also does the job. 
Happy riding - the weather will improve :))

:bike:

attachments.title: Love to Ride
attachments.text: Love to Ride is all about getting more people enjoying and discovering how easy and fun riding a bike can be. Whether you ride all the time, or you're new to riding, join the Love to Ride community, help grow cycling, make our neighborhoods more bike friendly, have some fun with your friends and win some great prizes.

text: Thanks for calling out the donation thing Felix! I had an account from last year and forgot about the account creation donation nag.

My next task is to plan a couple of happy hour rides during the month, so I'll do a bit of research and make a poll... Please suggest good days/venues! I'm thinking of doing one next week and another in the 4th week, different days, different paths, a nice 1ish mile ride on the east side to some place with interesting snacks and libations.
